<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>that’s life • this is the life</xh5><p> <i>that’s life</i>—(also: such is life) that’s the way things happen <i>(said with the implication that unpleasant events occur occasionally): </i>It’s a pity Colin and Rowena got divorced, but then <u>that’s life</u>!</p><p> <i>this is the life</i>—(exclam.) used as an admiring comment on a comfortable, enjoyable, and carefree existence: A sandy beach, plenty of hot sun, lots of nice people! <u>This is the life</u>!</p></entry>
